Kung Fu Hustle;;89;;91;;R;;When the hapless Sing (Stephen Chow) and his dim-witted pal, Bone (Feng Xiaogang), try to scam the residents of Pig Sty Alley into thinking they're members of the dreaded Axe Gang, the real gangsters descend on this Shanghai slum to restore their fearsome reputation. What gang leader Brother Sum (Danny Chan) doesn't know is that three legendary retired kung fu masters (Yu Xing, Dong Zhihua, Chiu Chi-ling) live anonymously in this decrepit neighborhood and don't take kindly to interlopers.;;Fantasy,Action,Comedy,Sports & fitness;;Stephen Chow;;2005;;Stephen Chow,Yuen Wah,Yuen Qiu,Siu-Lung Leung,Dong Zhihua,Chiu Chi-ling,Yu Xing,Danny Chan Kwok-Kwan,Eva Huang,Feng Xiao-Gang,Suet Lam,Hsiao Liang,Chi Chung Lam;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kung_fu_hustle